description:
Are you prepping for medical crises at home during the time of no buy no sell? Walt Cross looks at survival medicine to help you handle the top 10 health problems at home when you don’t have access to healthcare. Find out how to treat common problems like hypertension, arthritis, diabetes, pneumonia, ear infections, back pain, dermatitis and more.
